text:
South Korea goes from #1 world leader in #coronavirus cases to falling off map in just a month. WHY? They tested everyone & targeted quarantine/ treatment. USA can’t even test all sick in hospitals. So we went from barely on map to #1.
https://t.co/vKxo6m0rQt
